    <div class="docs-section">
      <h3>Socket.IO Events</h3>
      <p>All events are scoped per agent. Client subscribes with <code>socket.on('agent:&lt;agentId&gt;:&lt;event&gt;', handler)</code>.</p>
      <table class="docs-table">
        <thead><tr><th>Event suffix</th><th>Payload</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>tool-call</td><td>{ callId, tool, args }</td></tr>
          <tr><td>tool-result</td><td>{ callId, tool, success, error? }</td></tr>
          <tr><td>memory-update</td><td>{ type, data } — types: conversation, knowledge, knowledge-deleted, cleared</td></tr>
          <tr><td>tuning-update</td><td>{ systemPrompt, adjustableParams, config }</td></tr>
          <tr><td>action-new</td><td>AgentAction document</td></tr>
          <tr><td>background-status</td><td>{ status: started | stopped | tick, lastRun?, runCount? }</td></tr>
          <tr><td>push</td><td>{ type, title, content, actionId } — proactive message injected into chat</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

  </div>
